</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="219">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">14:</emphasis>
Material aus Spanien (4 B-Chromosomen 
<normalizedToken originalValue="gezählt" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">gezaehlt</normalizedToken>
; Baez-Mayor 1934), aus Schleswig-Holstein (Wulff 1937b), aus Island (
<normalizedToken originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1956b), aus den USA (Easterly 1963), aus Indien (Raj 1965).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="219">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, selten subalpin. Offene, stickstoffreiche 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Schuttplätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Schuttplaetze</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
, um 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Häuser" pageId="null" pageNumber="219">Haeuser</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="219">
